  <title>移动方块</title>
  
  <section id="move-piece">
    <title>移动方块</title>
    <p>为了移动一个方块，你可以点击选中它，然后点击要放置它的方格，或者把它拖动到方格里。</p>
    <p>这些移动并不是永久的，可以恢复。</p>
    <note>
      <p>
        The pieces in the left box can be moved all at once in one direction. Press the menu button in the
        top-right corner of the window and select <gui style="menuitem">Keyboard Shortcuts</gui> for more information.
      </p>
    </note>
  </section>
